Ned Nwoko is celebrating 10 years of being with his Moroccan wife as he counts down to her 30th birthday. Taking to his Instagram handle, Ned Nwoko shared a photo of himself and Laila Charani Nwoko. He captioned the photo: “Laila will be 30 years in a few days time. It feels like yesterday. It has been ten beautiful years. Amazing how she has matured over the years.”  Laila Charani and Ned Nwoko share 3 children together. Laila is stepmother to Ned’s other kids from his other wives, including Regina Daniels.